# AI Agent Rules

## Knowledge Base MCP
This project integrates with a personal Knowledge Base via MCP.

## Workflow
- Save notes, summaries, research to knowledge base via save_document
- Search prior knowledge via search_documents
- Review past AI conversations via list_conversations / get_conversation
- Organize documents with folders and tags
- Use MCP as the only official sync path
- For structured records, prefer save_document / update_document
- On compression or reset, create a Snapshot Doc and update the Daily Digest
- Resolve target folders by logical path, never by hardcoded folderId
- When updating task, topic, decision, or daily docs, read existing content first and merge incrementally
